D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to gather, assemble, keep together, to collect","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"ويشار بحسب المجلة، بان اعداد إرهابيي داعش الأجانب ما زال كبيرا جدا على الرغم من التقديرات التي ترجح مقتل الآلاف منهم، حيث تظهر البيانات المجموعة من 33 دولة لها مواطنين يقاتلون مع عصابات داعش الإرهابية، ان ما يزيد عن 6000 منهم قد تمكنوا من العودة الى بلدانهم، فيما تصل اعداد الغائبين إلى الآلاف المضاعفة.","english":"It is shown by the magazine that the number of foreign ISIS terrorists has not ceased to be very large in spite of assessments that affirm the death of thousands of them as likely, whereas the data gathered from 33 states to which citizens fighting for terrorist ISIS groups belong reveals that more than 6000 of them have had the opportunity of returning to their homelands, while the number of absentees has reached several thousands."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to unite, to reconcile","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect oneself, to recollect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lie with"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to add"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to form the plural"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to contain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be full-grown"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have two or more negative attributes at the same time; to have a negative attribute on top of another negative attribute","examples":[{"text":"جَمَعَ بَيْنَ الْجَهْلِ وَﺳُﻮء الْخُلُق","english":"Not only was he ignorant but also ill-mannered"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to assemble","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَمَعَ (jamaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gathering, collecting","examples":[{"text":"جَمْعُ المَال","english":"raising money; collecting money"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crowd, throng, mass, legion","examples":[{"text":"جَمْعٌ مِنَ النَاس","english":"a gathering of people"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a military force"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural, a form of a noun denoting multiples by its sense","examples":[{"text":"جَمْع رُوح أَرْوَاح","english":"the plural of \"rūḥ\" is \"arwāḥ\""}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"addition","examples":[{"text":"الجَمْع وَالطَرْح","english":"addition and subtraction"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lumping together, putting subjects in the same category"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a proposition in which a general and a particular subject are included in one category or judgement through a common attribute"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distribution of a term"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Harsusi [script needed] (egtōma), Mehri عَتمَأ (gatmaʾ).\n\nIntensive of جَمَعَ (jamaʕa)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.ma.ʕa/","/d͡ʒam.ma.ʕa/","/d͡ʒamʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6304","headword_ar":"جَمَعَ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected; brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered, together; gathered up; assembled; congregated; mustered; drew together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Er-Rághib, B, K; *) a thing; (Er-Rághib, Msb, B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the several parts or portions became near together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, B;) or a thing in a scattered, or dispersed, state; (Fr, S;) and a number of men; (Fr;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~E","text_ar":"جمّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [or this has only an intensive signification;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjmE","text_ar":"اجمع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also the inf. n.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below; and] see 2; and 10. ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa bayonahumaA","text_ar":"جَمَعَ بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought them two together, into a state of union, after separation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reconciled them; conciliated them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, united, connected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formed a connexion between, them two:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 3 (last sentence) in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dnw","text_ar":"دنو"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi viyaAbahu","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ ثِيَابَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attired himself with, his clothes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEati AljaAriyapu","text_ar":"جَمَعَتِ الجَارِيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The girl put on the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diroE","text_ar":"دِرْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaAr","text_ar":"خِمَار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miloHafap","text_ar":"مِلْحَفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) i. e., (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became a young woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became full-grown."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA jamaEotu","text_ar":"مَا جَمَعْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@moraA^apK qaT~u","text_ar":"بِا@مْرَاَةٍ قَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani A@moraA^apK","text_ar":"عَنِ ا@مْرَاَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have never gone in to a woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have never had a woman conducted to me as my bride."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA@jomaEuwA","text_ar":"فَا@جْمَعُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kayodakumo","text_ar":"كَيْدَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fajamaEa kayodahu","text_ar":"فَجَمَعَ كَيْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa A^amorahu","text_ar":"جَمَعَ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b8-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He composed, arranged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, or an affair; as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa A@ll~`hu $amolahu","text_ar":"جَمَعَ ا@للّٰهُ شَمْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ml","text_ar":"شمل"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b9-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It comprised, comprehended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contained."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b10-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pluralized"},{"kind":"text","text":"a word;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have a plural,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plurals."},{"kind":"text","text":"(The Lexicons passim.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","TA","K"]}]}}